The paper deals with online learning algorithms and their impact on different user groups, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study of externalities and their effects on different populations also involves data analysis and statistical inference (cs.DS), as well as information theory (cs.IT) and social networks (cs.SI).
